### GET all products - Obtener todos los contactos

GET http://localhost:3000/api/products/
Accept: application/json

###

### GET- Obtener un contacto por ID

GET http://localhost:3000/products/{{id}}
Accept: application/json

###

### POST a new product- Crear un nuevo producto (todos los campos requeridos)

POST http://localhost:3000/api/products/
Content-Type: application/json
{
"name": "Luxury",
"price": 55,
"description": "A luxurious scent for all genders"
}

###

### PUT update a product- Actualizar un contacto existente (todos los campos requeridos)

PUT http://localhost:3000/products/{{id}}
Content-Type: application/json
{
"name": "Updated Name",
"price": 60,
"description": "Updated description"
}

###

### DELETE a product- Eliminar un contacto

DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/products/{{id}}
Content-Type: application/json
